{"tid":588702,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［絲打入］哩段片阿佘係咪素顏？","createTime":"2018-03-11T11:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T19:38:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"12dbf0e462d79c30d12b0676a8097357ceef160b","tid":588702,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/194007_46ae0d609dff3d7452782a5679d53783.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F194007_46ae0d609dff3d7452782a5679d53783.png&h=0ac1faf2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/194008_87b6175193eda4516e380999ededdf1e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F194008_87b6175193eda4516e380999ededdf1e.png&h=c6e21d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/194033_41e49b684f534ed1b0e6f71671c4a780.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F194033_41e49b684f534ed1b0e6f71671c4a780.png&h=0812df45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/194035_625a8171590c0b3cc60aa3cd09e4d2df.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F194035_625a8171590c0b3cc60aa3cd09e4d2df.png&h=e4bf8060&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藝人佘詩曼（阿佘）早前夥拍黃子華的賀歲片《棟篤特工》、票房衝破四千萬！大感興奮的阿佘昨晚更鮮有地在家中廚房以素顏上陣，即興在社交平台開Live，與粉絲們舉行分享會。阿佘向來被網友公認為圈中數一數二的素顏美女，除了出席公開活動外，她社交平台上的大部分日常生活照，例如搭飛機、用餐時，統統都是沒有化妝，皮膚總是白裹透紅，臉上永遠掛着甜到漏的笑容，連藝人黃子華在多次訪問中，也說很佩服阿佘可以通宵達旦開工，翌日早上個個都想殺人般的面口，唯獨這位拍檔仍然可以笑臉迎人，連身邊對手也被她感染到如沐春風一樣⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180311/mobile/bkn-20180311140939436-0311_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180311%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180311140939436-0311_00862_001.html&d=%2F4C5RZOQNvE4NBHarc2ArkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b4971eab\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180311/mobile/bkn-20180311140939436-0311_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n東方話係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果素顏都咁白滑真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原片（有sell唔知咩雞精,慎入）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/charmainesss/videos/957470334422172/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcharmainesss%2Fvideos%2F957470334422172%2F&d=%2F4C5RZOQNvE4NBHarc2ArkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=8d67d14b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/charmainesss/videos/957470334422172/</a>"},{"pid":"00cfc19b671cf0b4bf0f3c41164eb6c6ddb4407b","tid":588702,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T11:46:59.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n利申巴"},{"pid":"e0ee6b15cbd6f665dd16f9b21c16710ca443dfc2","tid":588702,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00cfc19b671cf0b4bf0f3c41164eb6c6ddb4407b","tid":588702,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T11:46:59.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n利申巴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點睇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6871ebd25465adb89a1c9a795b4732d2a721206d","tid":588702,"uid":90969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T11:51:12.000Z","msg":"可能係紋左眉紋左眼線既素顏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif